710707f-a.title: Manhattan: 11th Avenue - 44th Street (West)
710707f-a.text:
Eleventh Avenue, east side, south from West 45th
Street. Most of this area has been cleared as a
part of the track removal program of the New
York Central R.R. Nos. 586-580, at, adjoining
and south of the S.E. corner of 44th Street, are
still standing. Shown across clearance, is West
44th Street, at, adjoining and east of the S.E.
corner of Eleventh Avenue.
View 2 shows the same area, at a later date.
P. L. Sperr  View 1: Dec. 4, 1936
NO REPRODUCTIONS  View 2: Sept. 4, 1940
